{"tid":1926863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到啲連登仔成日吹奏公屋好撚好笑","createTime":"2020-03-15T11:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T16:50:16.000Z","uid":337986,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6de09e72aa658e6b9060b9b189dd43301b58a9d7","tid":1926863,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:33:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔又話住公屋去埃及去旅行好撚有錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去埃及好撚貴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打份垃圾工都去得起<br />\n連登仔又話公屋停車場入面好多靚車好撚有錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有車=靚車 垃圾二手寶馬audi落地唔知幾多十年幾萬蚊就買到 起碼Aston Martin Bently 呢啲先叫靚車啦on99 <br />\n見到公屋撚揸波子林寶又話好撚有錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上二手車網睇下啲舊款垃圾波子值幾萬蚊咋落地幾多十年林寶好撚貴呀on99?而家有車=有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n好心班連登仔得閒出入高級住宅停車場睇下咩叫靚車啦 幾萬蚊就買到就叫靚車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚寒酸好撚冇眼光<br />\n<br />\n咩人會吹奏公屋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公屋仔咪吹奏公屋囉<br />\n成日話住公屋點點點有錢點點點隱形富豪 識人住公屋有幾百萬個啲一定係住公屋驚死人睇唔起自己而吹奏公屋既自卑撚<br />\n有錢人住公屋 咁誠哥係咪住係啲甩皮甩骨既垃圾公屋呀？律師醫生呢？住公屋呀？大公司老闆係唔撚係全部住公屋呀？有錢人都住豪宅獨立屋啦 講嘢都唔撚用腦？ 自卑到冇撚左個腦定點？定覺得戶口有幾十萬又叫富豪呀？買個Hermes袋都冇撚左啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話公屋有富豪就好似你話藍絲入面有黃絲一樣咁撚on9</span></span>"},{"pid":"62166ba9aa6052e98ec2e911c803c4e921e0bad9","tid":1926863,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"駁吾刀 利申冇申請公屋資格"},{"pid":"59df065eb648c73338592a62d7c8527b768da7cb","tid":1926863,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"有兩個住公屋既連登仔靜靜雞負皮<br />\n話我知住公屋可以有幾撚有錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請司機？出入賓利定有私人飛機 戴開百達翡麗？<br />\n想知有咩富豪富豪住公屋咁撚巴閉呀<br />\n李澤楷定馬化騰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402a93e6eec574e8ac56741f2f953d399e3f8388","tid":1926863,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"國際學校有冇公屋撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n富豪排名榜頭一萬位有冇公屋撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身家過億會唔會住公屋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公屋撚點撚樣有錢法姐 出聲啦公屋富豪<br />\n負皮完就走又唔撚出聲<br />\n自卑到縮左入老母個系到？"},{"pid":"105c7b2e9465b7453cf19dd5b9ea3161f4ea95f4","tid":1926863,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:51:09.000Z","msg":"公屋撚出黎啦<br />\n邊個月入過十萬既仲住公屋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟公屋撚有幾有錢呀？<br />\n揸架垃圾殘舊寶馬audi benz波子=富豪？<br />\n出街威完 條女上到自己屋企都即刻濕唔撚起啦<br />\n見到你架垃圾車濕先定係見到豪宅濕先呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公屋有富豪 不如你話雞場有處女啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ea87e688f756b0560ec8c9d52ac21beea0a33ab","tid":1926863,"uid":312758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:52:22.000Z","msg":"真心...<br />\n想住公屋都無機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b68f167b1462b46a4fae02dead6ff414b21decc","tid":1926863,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ea87e688f756b0560ec8c9d52ac21beea0a33ab","tid":1926863,"uid":312758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:52:22.000Z","msg":"真心...<br />\n想住公屋都無機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"因為你唔夠有錢<br />\n住公屋都係富豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8401b871cb93a0174f05df265ba3592b938f1205","tid":1926863,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"105c7b2e9465b7453cf19dd5b9ea3161f4ea95f4","tid":1926863,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"